Ase0SelectedOnlyCmdDesc: Show the selected elements and hide all other elements.
Ase0SystemRequirementsSplitAllDesc: View all requirements in the structure.
Ase0SystemRequirementsSplitBottomDesc: View only the requirements that have attributes.
Ase0SystemRequirementsSplitGroupDesc: View or hide requirements in the structure.
Ase0SystemRequirementsSplitOffDesc: View only requirements that do not have attributes or documents.
Ase0SystemRequirementsSplitRightDesc: View only requirements that have attributes or documents.
Ase0DeleteAnnotationsDesc: Remove the selected annotations from the diagram.
Ase0SaveAsDiagramDesc: Save the diagram with a new name. This is useful for duplicating a diagram.
Ase0SetAutoLayoutDesc: Activate to automatically organize elements. Deactivate to manually organize and align elements.
ShowSplitPanelGroupDesc: Specify a location to display the Interface Details panel.
ShowSplitPanelRightDesc: Display the interfaces to the right of the diagram.
ShowSplitPanelBottomDesc: View the panel below the diagram.
showAssociatedItemsPanelDesc: View the diagrams associated with the selected node.
ase0InverseSelectionCommandDesc: Clear the current selections and select the unselected elements.
Ase0AlignCommandGroupDesc: Select nodes and then select an alignment.
Ase0AlignTopDesc: Align the top sides of the nodes to the top-most node.
Ase0AlignBottomDesc: Align the bottom sides of the nodes relative to the bottom-most node.
Ase0AlignRightDesc: Align the left sides of the nodes relative to the left-most node.
Ase0AlignMiddleDesc: Align the nodes relative to their vertical centers.
Ase0GridDesc: Toggle between major and minor grid line types.
Ase0ConvertToParentCmdDesc: Convert the selected node to parent node
Ase0VisibilityControlGroupCmdDesc: Set the visibility of the diagram, ports, and connections.
Ase0FitCmdDesc: Fit all the elements in the display area.
Ase0FitSelectedCmdDesc: Fit and center the elements in the display area.
Ase0ShowAllPortsDesc: Display all ports in the diagram, including orphan (disconnected) ports.
Ase0HideParentCmdDesc: Hide the parent of this node.
Ase0ShowParentCmdDesc: View the parent relation for this node.
Ase0ShowConnectedPortsDesc: Display the connected ports only. Orphan (disconnected) ports are hidden.
Ase0SetAsAnchorDesc: Set the selected element as the root element.
Ase0NestedViewDesc: View elements in the nested (box in box) view, where child elements are shown within parent elements.
Ase0NetworkViewDesc: View elements in the network view.
Ase0ShowLabelDesc: Show labels for all or selected elements.
Ase0HideLabelDesc: Turn on or off the label display.
Ase0ResetLabelPositionDesc: Restore all or the selected labels back to their default positions.
Ase0ShowObjectRelationsDesc: View the connections and trace links.
Ase0ReconnectConnectionDesc: Reconnect the selected connection to a system block or a port.
Ase0ExpandAllRelationsDesc: Expand the selected node by one level.
Ase0OpenCreateTracelinkPanelDesc: Open the create trace link panel
Ase0DeleteRequirementTracelinkDesc: Delete trace link associated with selected Requirement.
showObjectsInACEListDesc: Toggle the display of connections and ports in the structure
